        "step_2_title": "Set",
        "step_2_body": "<p>Lightly sweep powder across the face to lock in makeup and control shine. Focus on oily areas like the forehead, nose, and around the eyes.</p>",
        "step_3_number": "3",
        "step_3_title": "Touch up",
        "step_3_body": "<p>Use throughout the day to refresh makeup and reduce shine without buildup. Perfect for quick on-the-go mattifying.</p>",
