        "body": "<p>Our award-winning setting powder combines cutting-edge technology with clean, skin-caring ingredients. The weightless formula creates a soft-focus finish that photographs beautifully—perfect for everyday wear or special events.</p>",
        "check_icon_size": 18,
        "item_1": "<p><strong>Invisible Finish:</strong> Ultra-fine milled powder blurs imperfections without looking cakey or settling into fine lines.</p>",
        "item_2": "<p><strong>All-Day Wear:</strong> Locks in your makeup for 16+ hours while controlling oil and shine.</p>",
        "item_3": "<p><strong>Skin-Perfecting Formula:</strong> Infused with light-reflecting pearls and skin-loving ingredients for a luminous, airbrushed effect.</p>",
        "item_4": "<p><strong>Universal Shade Range:</strong> 8 expertly curated shades designed to complement every skin tone without oxidising or changing color.</p>",
